    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031480/extras/6caf40071086464000e5b56bbe33edcc.avif?t=1728541191\" width=620 height=102 /></span><strong>“東方幕華祭 永夜篇”现已上线商店页！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031480/extras/8755f1c15206727db0d5ab1f2155052e.avif?t=1728541191\" width=616 height=200 /></span>東方幕華祭 春雪篇 ~ Fantastic Danmaku Festival Part Ⅱ 是一款弹幕射击游戏。東方幕華祭系列的第二作，异变重演现象再度来袭，前往冥界的少女们这次能否揭开谜底？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >★键盘操作</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >方向键 人物移动</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Z 射击 / 确认</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >X 发动符卡(Bomb) / 取消</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shift 低速移动</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Esc 暂停游戏</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >★手柄操作</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>请在游戏开始前强制关闭Steam输入以免无法启动原生手柄支持</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持XboX 360，Xbox One以及Playstation4手柄，你可以在游戏启动器中选择默认的键位设置</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同时也支持大多数其他控制器，如果你遇到失去控制的情况，尝试在手柄设置中设置移动阈值</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >★故事背景</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031480/extras/20f0787301845788d413e073d52e358b.avif?t=1728541191\" width=616 height=100 /></span>幻想乡的春天已经到来了一个月……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >史无前例的暴风雪突然降临，使整个幻想乡变得比冬天更加寒冷。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没过多久，在遮天蔽日的暴雪中，妖怪们也变得不安分起来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“太相似了……这不会是巧合吧？”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >神社的巫女，森林的魔法使，特地赶来的风祝。少女们再次聚在一起，彼此心领神会却又充满疑惑和不安。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了在情况更加恶化之前解决它，就算是冒着暴风雪——还是要出发去寻找一下异变的源头吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >★新角色设定</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031480/extras/23bb11eceb94e00ca4dea98fb3df2d74.avif?t=1728541191\" width=616 height=100 /></span>○纯白游荡者</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <strong>修普</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <strong>Hyp</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    种族：不明</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    能力：使人睡着的能力</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    浮游在大雪纷飞的天空中，被纯白的巨大羽翼包裹的谜之白色猫头鹰妖怪（?），因为有适应雪天的保护色而难以察觉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    枕头中的羽毛掉出后变成了雪，使得幻想乡的暴雪又加重了一点点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    自称为了觅食才在雪夜里出现，但却很懒，会在战斗中睡着。看起来实力并不强的样子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >○甜蜜与芳香的妖精</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <strong>莉莉·怀特</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <strong>Lily White</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    种族：妖精</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    能力：告知春天来临的能力</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    被祭典主办者安排在冥界入口迎接参加祭典的客人的妖精，为此盛装打扮了一番。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    有点神志不清，利用获得的来历不明的新力量对没有[邀请函]的来者疯狂攻击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >★关于魂魄妖梦</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031480/extras/2886c0994d600d8d904736bd973f056f.avif?t=1728541191\" width=616 height=100 /></span>在白玉楼看似平常的一日，妖梦被幽幽子莫名其妙的提出了去人间之里采购的要求。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“你知道我跑一趟人间之里要花多少时间吗”虽然妖梦这么吐槽，还是拿幽幽子没办法，乖乖出门了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但来到地上后，离奇的暴雪却让妖梦彻底傻眼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在连续问了数个冒雪上山砍柴的樵夫后，妖梦总算确认地上现在真的是春天。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人间之里家家户户闭门不出，令妖梦的采购之行彻底泡汤，但更糟糕的是幻想乡的暴雪中无数妖怪开始暴动起来……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >★游戏亮点</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031480/extras/59f52ed43ca82eed290dc6f7e4f18cfc.avif?t=1728541191\" width=616 height=100 /></span><strong>-看似熟悉却截然不同的全新剧情。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-华美与挑战性并存的关卡演出和弹幕，为你带来不同于传统飞行射击游戏的视觉体验。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-时隔5年的系列续作，挑战弹幕的极限。</strong></p>",
